data.description: $15k Buyer Credit for Interest Rate Buy-down!(see agent for details)  Beautiful city lights & mountain views, excellent location, light and bright home, open & split floor plans, w/2nd Living Qtrs, RV Pkg & Solar for LOW electric bills! This desirable floor plan has thoughtful details providing many reasons to love this home the moment you walk in. Primary Bdrm has a huge walk-in closet, slider to deck w/views & Bathrm w/dual vanity, jetted tub, separate shower & toilet rm. Kitchen has granite countertops, Dbl ovens, built-in range/microwave, pull-out shelves, ample storage, dbl basin sink & Lg pantry cupboard. On the other side of the home is an office, 2bdms/1ba all w/high ceilings.  2nd living quarters downstairs has its own driveway, pkg, private entrance, covered porch, kitchen, 1 bdrm, bathroom, living & family rooms.  Sep workshop/storage below. Spacious attch'd 2car gar has sink.  Small golf putting green. Desirable neighborhood & easy access to Dist 7 schools,/town/river/I-5
